name: fcall command
command:
function load "#!lua name=mylib 
 redis.register_function('myfunc', function(keys, args) return args[1] end)"

name: fcall_ro command
command:
function load "#!lua name=mylib 
 local function ret(keys, args) return args[1] end 
 redis.register_function{function_name='ret', callback=ret, flags={ 'no-writes' }}"
